A 46 year old married man from Limpopo was arrested yesterday for masturbating to pictures of himself in public.Frank Nyathi was caught by a group of teenagers outside a tavern in Mokopane with his pants down and his hand on his manhood, while he intimately helped himself to a picture of himself in the wee hours of yesterday morning.The SAPS confirmed that the man has been arrested and a case has been opened. &#8220;He was not that drunk. We knew he loved himself so much, but we did not think he would take it that far. More pictures of himself were found in his pockets when he was arrested.&#8221;one of his friends. His wife and kids are still shocked and will be taken for counseling, a local newspaper revealed.